  <front>
    <title>Host Identity Protocol (HIP) Registration Extension</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-ietf-hip-rfc5203-bis-04"/>
    <author initials="J." surname="Laganier" fullname="Julien Laganier"/>
    <author initials="L." surname="Eggert" fullname="Lars Eggert"/>
    <date day="14" month="January" year="2014"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies a registration mechanism for the Host
   Identity Protocol (HIP) that allows hosts to register with services,
   such as HIP rendezvous servers or middleboxes.  This document
   obsoletes RFC5203.

	 </t>
    </abstract>
